={"model":"chat-max","stream":false,"options":{"temperature":0.4,"num_predict":2048},"prompt":"Translate the text from {{ $json.source }} to {{ $json.target }}. Style: {{ $json.style }}. CRITICAL: do NOT translate word-for-word — adapt idioms, native phrasing, cultural fit. Keep brand names (AdOff, uBlock Origin, etc.) untranslated. Preserve URLs and code. Output ONLY the translated text, no preamble.

--- SOURCE ({{ $json.source }}) ---
{{ $json.text }}
--- END ---

Translated ({{ $json.target }}):"}

